{"tid":131332,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"資金衝香港！社保基金已開始掃港股","createTime":"2017-02-23T04:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-23T12:33:51.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fde7e4da9a407994136e295e601a9893f1eddd5b","tid":131332,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:15:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/23/121238_0d7ffc759fb51ca9baa2d8eaa1ddffc2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F23%2F121238_0d7ffc759fb51ca9baa2d8eaa1ddffc2.jpg&h=fbf29f44&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n國泰君安（1788）國際董事會主席閻峰，接受彭博訪問時表示，中國社保基金已買入港股，以獲得更高回報。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，國泰君安和其香港部門已經為中國社保基金購入A股和港股提供投資建議和交易服務。<br />\n<br />\n今年以來，港股持續火熱。年初至今，恒生指數累計漲幅約10%，領跑全球。此前的分析稱，正是中資推動了港股的上漲。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56342416&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170223\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56342416%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170223&d=mHuePEBkC2D1nBcDBUtULzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=abc420b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56342416%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170223&h=49361feb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56342416&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170223</a><br />\n<br />\n//諗起沈大師22000話夾淡倉，夾咗2千點仲係夾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c4a85579954f5a2da48207b58b5196af3a9d64","tid":131332,"uid":54481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:16:23.000Z","msg":"24600 gogogo"},{"pid":"71e14c46725ecdfc9ce85109e8ed48aa38f2cf20","tid":131332,"uid":71655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T04:17: