易所有限公司證券上市規則第 13.09 條作出。<br />\n<br />\n本公司注意到最近有媒體報道指本集團董事會主席兼行政總裁閻峰博士對全國社會保障基金近期投資港股作出了評論。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">本公司謹此澄清，截止本公告日期，閻峰博士或本公司並無對全國社會保障基金近期投資港股（若有）事宜發表任何評論。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n股東及本公司潛在投資者於買賣本公司股份時應審慎行事。"},{"pid":"04ff35d4259632228132684fe7f85a7979d3e0a8","tid":131332,"uid":67280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:08:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家人人都睇升<br />\n所以我覺得係時候留意幾時應該走<br />\n冇set target<br />\n日日睇圖<br />\n唔對路就走<br />\n<br />\n我係咁操作</blockquote><br />\n大戶起碼夾埋你個put先落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04b8aa5fce64ef3cd3e8ab954794979059c27d18","tid":131332,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:14:06.000Z","msg":"有5萬點，支持中央直接委任香港書記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e56e903bb9e00e57ed76e94cfaca30759cb125b6","tid":131332,"uid":26619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:28:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有5萬點，支持中央直接委任香港書記<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n升到5萬，邊個做特首無所謂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2dadfbbf9d51e11065e54915a0505647031a2c2","tid":131332,"uid":63450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而家人人都睇升<br />\n所以我覺得係時候留意幾時應該走<br />\n冇set target<br />\n日日睇圖<br />\n唔對路就走<br />\n<br />\n我係咁操作</blockquote><br />\n我同你睇法差唔多<br />\n不過操作上簡單好多<br />\n大師講咩我買相反就ok了"},{"pid":"625c2d2e4d9a1eafef1e43dd838534b803c673b8","tid":131332,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T11:57:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2712254c6d76baa203e33a3aa50e962797b87c4","tid":131332,"uid":50310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-23T12:33:51.000Z",